Get dsSrc data from google sheet

Source: R/dssrc_dataframe.R
dssrc_dataframe.Rd

The dsSrc dataset is maintained by Julie and contains most of the relevant onboarding information.

Usage

dssrc_dataframe()

Examples

dssrc = dssrc_dataframe()
